We are married for almost 2 years and we were in a relationship for almost 10 years.  
Now, my wife is in Europe for study and I am in my homeland Bangladesh. Couldn’t go with her because of a visa issue. When I listen to Jhol, the memory of my happy time starts to appear in a very Colorful and Vivid way. Although I hardly understand the lyrics. 
Thanks for the wonderful song man.
